---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us | Surrey Contracting Limited"
  description="Contact Surrey Contracting Limited to request a quote for groundworks, earthworks or surfacing across Surrey. Call 01932 932650."
  path="/contact"
  active="contact"
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="page-hero-img" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/hard-landscaping.jpg')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-vignette"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container page-hero-inner">
    <nav class="crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      <span>Contact Us</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="page-title">Get in touch</h1>
    <p class="page-lede">Tell us about your site and we'll be back inside one working day with a measured visit date.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container contact-grid">
    <div class="contact-info">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-yellow">Talk to a contracts manager</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Real people with real experience.</h2>
      <p>From quote to handover, one person, one point of contact from end to end. No tickets, no escalations, no being passed around.</p>

      <div class="contact-cards">
        <div class="contact-card">
          <div class="contact-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.86 19.86 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.86 19.86 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.36 1.9.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.91.34 1.85.57 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <span class="contact-label">Call us</span>
            <a class="contact-value" href="tel:01932932650">01932 932650</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-card">
          <div class="contact-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 22s7-7 7-12a7 7 0 1 0-14 0c0 5 7 12 7 12z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2.5"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <span class="contact-label">Yard</span>
            <span class="contact-value">Surrey Contracting Limited, Upper Leewood Farm Yard,<br>Effingham Common Road, Leatherhead, KT24 5JQ</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-card">
          <div class="contact-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 3"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <span class="contact-label">Hours</span>
            <span class="contact-value">Mon-Fri 07:30-17:30<br>Out-of-hours: by arrangement</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <form class="quote-form contact-form" id="quoteForm" novalidate>
      <div style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;width:1px;height:1px;overflow:hidden;" aria-hidden="true">
        <label>Company website<input type="text" name="_honeypot" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off"></label>
      </div>
      <h3 class="form-title">Send us a message</h3>
      <div class="qf-row">
        <label><span>Name</span><input required name="name" type="text" placeholder="Your full name"></label>
        <label><span>Phone</span><input required name="phone" type="tel" placeholder="01932 932650"></label>
      </div>
      <label><span>Email</span><input required name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@email.com"></label>
      <label><span>Company / organisation</span><input name="company" type="text" placeholder="Optional"></label>
      <fieldset class="qf-checks">
        <legend>What do you need?</legend>
        <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" name="svc" value="Demolition"><span>Demolition</span></label>
        <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" name="svc" value="Groundworks"><span>Groundworks</span></label>
        <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" name="svc" value="Bulk Earthworks"><span>Bulk Earthworks</span></label>
        <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" name="svc" value="Commercial Surfacing"><span>Commercial Surfacing</span></label>
        <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" name="svc" value="Driveways"><span>Driveways &amp; Paving</span></label>
        <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" name="svc" value="Other"><span>Other</span></label>
      </fieldset>
      <label><span>Project postcode</span><input name="postcode" type="text" placeholder="GU1 1AA"></label>
      <label><span>Tell us about the job</span><textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Site type, scale, target start date…"></textarea></label>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-yellow btn-block">Send enquiry</button>
      <p class="qf-success" id="qfSuccess" hidden>Thanks, we've got it. A contracts manager will be in touch within one working day.</p>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section page-section-dark">
  <div class="container areas-grid">
    <div class="areas-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-yellow">Where we work</span>
      <h2 class="section-title light">Surrey, London &amp; the South East.</h2>
      <p>Headquartered between Cobham and Leatherhead, Surrey Contracting operates across Surrey, London and the South East. We are ideally positioned to support projects throughout the M25 corridor, along the A3 and across the surrounding counties, providing a reliable and responsive service for commercial, residential and development-led works.</p>
      <ul class="areas-list">
        <li>Cobham</li><li>Leatherhead</li><li>Guildford</li><li>Esher</li>
        <li>Woking</li><li>Reigate</li><li>Dorking</li><li>Epsom</li>
        <li>Weybridge</li><li>Kingston</li><li>Redhill</li><li>Surbiton</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="areas-map" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="map-frame">
        <img src="/assets/img/coverage-map.png" alt="Coverage map" class="map-img">
        <div class="map-pin">
          <span class="pin-dot"></span>
          <span class="pin-ring"></span>
          <span class="pin-label">HQ · Leatherhead</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
